data.title: Big Birthday: Tom Cruise is 60
data.meta_description: Born on the 3rd of July, he proved himself as an actor in Born on the 4th of July. From Outsiders to Top Gun: Maverick and everything in between: the franchises, the comedies, the dramas, Cruise did it all. Some Risky Business with Eyes Wide Shut, he accomplished his Mission: Impossible – becoming a Hollywood star and remaining on top.
